farmworkers and colonia communities

   We've created this page for Farm workers and Colonia Communities. It
   contains information from all parts of HUD's web site, that will
   interest you. We hope you will bookmark this page and return to it
   frequently.

   We've also created a list of farm worker and colonia specialists at
   HUD. These individuals and others can assist with your special needs.
   Click here for a list of HUD contacts.


